            "title": "人行今進行5億元人幣逆回購 淨回籠780億",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">人民銀行昨日在公開市場進行5億元(人民幣‧下同)的7天期逆回購操作，操作利率持平於1.40%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">計入今日有785億元逆回購到期，人行於公開市場今日淨回籠780億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15821859-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%e4%bb%8a%e9%80%b2%e8%a1%8c5%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3%e9%80%86%e5%9b%9e%e8%b3%bc-%e6%b7%a8%e5%9b%9e%e7%b1%a0780%e5%84%84",
