            "title": "即月期指開報25325點 高水537點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月期指開報25325點，升570點，較上日現貨收市價24788點高水537點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月科指期貨開報4777點，升138點，高水127點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">即月國指期貨開報8544點，升187點，高水170點。</p>\n</div>",
